Interface SerializableSupplier<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.util.function.Supplier<T>
    Functional Interface:

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface SerializableSupplier<T>
extends java.util.function.Supplier<T>, java.io.Serializable
    A union of a Supplier and Serializable, enabling configuration with T types that are not Serializable.
